  "description": "This dataset presents a comprehensive methodology for sample enrichment in electroencephalography (EEG) biomarker studies designed to classify Alzheimer's disease risk. The study involves EEG recordings from participants selected through a systematic enrichment protocol to optimize biomarker identification and classification accuracy for cognitive decline and dementia risk assessment.",
